data.description: Absolutely fantastic 3 bedroom 2 bath home  sitting on 2.25 acres just outside of town. Opportunities in this sought after school district and community RARELY even make it to market! Wonderful neighborhood with less than a dozen homes giving you plenty of space and privacy with the convenience of living just outside of town. The home is beautifully updated with GORGEOUS hardwoods, beautiful crown moulding, stainless appliances, granite countertops, walk-in shower and more! The rooms are nice and spacious and the partially finished basement will allow you to finish the home with YOUR own touch! Off the back there is a LARGE deck space with a beautiful park -like view to enjoy your coffee, cocktails, or BBQ with friends and family. This one checks all the boxes, don't let it slip away!
